%h1 Blog
%p While I don't expect I'll be writing a best-seller any time soon, I do occasionally like to showcase my work, and offer tips and insights into the world of web design and development.
%section.article-list
  - articles_by_month.each_pair do |month,articles|
    .article-group
      %h2= month
      %ul
        - articles.each do |article|
          %li
            %span= link_to article.title, article.url
            %span.date= article.date.strftime date.format